1
00:00:00,560 --> 00:00:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou!</font>

2
00:00:01,930 --> 00:00:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's already well into the fire hour.</font>

3
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times have I told you 
to take proper meal breaks?</font>

4
00:00:07,570 --> 00:00:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I got absorbed in my work 
since I haven't done any in so long.</font>

5
00:00:12,270 --> 00:00:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Aresh-san.</font>

6
00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up.</font>

7
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yesterday, he demanded that
 I change the way I speak to him.</i></font>

8
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For now, as a compromise, we've agreed 
that I would use his name differently.</i></font>

9
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never expected something so small
to improve his mood so much.</i></font>

10
00:00:34,260 --> 00:00:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then, I'll be...</font>

11
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're coming with us.</font>

12
00:00:39,210 --> 00:00:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have some tsuhash soup, too.</font>

13
00:00:42,050 --> 00:00:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I join you, as well?</font>

14
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The same old pattern...</i></font>

15
00:00:50,380 --> 00:00:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing seems amiss with the
financial report the church submitted.</font>

16
00:00:54,250 --> 00:00:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, the report itself seems fine.</font>

17
00:00:57,070 --> 00:01:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I received your write-up,
 as well. Good work.</font>

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was nothing. Just doing my job.</font>

19
00:01:05,210 --> 00:01:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right. With this, 
my special assignment is over.</i></font>

20
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While I'd love to take a breather now 
that we've finally contained the miasma,</font>

21
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we simply cannot afford to leave 
this situation unaddressed.</font>

22
00:01:17,670 --> 00:01:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, you mentioned something 
about magical energy...</font>

23
00:01:20,650 --> 00:01:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assume we can put that
information to use, as well?</font>

24
00:01:23,450 --> 00:01:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He wants me to help him 
put a leash on the church.</i></font>

25
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However...</i></font>

26
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give me a break.</font>

27
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm clueless when it comes
to political maneuvering.</font>

28
00:01:37,310 --> 00:01:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will submit the results 
of my cross-checking</font>

29
00:01:39,450 --> 00:01:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the accounting department's 
records against the list of nobles</font>

30
00:01:42,650 --> 00:01:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who allegedly didn't make donations 
despite being in the worship logs.</font>

31
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I'd ask the legal 
department to handle the matter</font>

32
00:01:49,170 --> 00:01:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of anyone whose name has been erased.</font>

33
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Furthermore, regarding the magical energy 
specially collected by the chapel...</font>

34
00:01:57,220 --> 00:02:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sorcery department is currently 
developing a tool capable of quantifying</font>

35
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the amount of magic necessary 
for the barrier spell.</font>

36
00:02:03,750 --> 00:02:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once they confirm the 
efficacy of the device</font>

37
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">through various organizations
that use a lot of magic tools,</font>

38
00:02:08,550 --> 00:02:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be able to provide you
 with the final product.</font>

39
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very good.</font>

40
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're truly magnificent, Seichiro.</font>

41
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you ever grow weary of that black 
beast over there, be sure to let me know.</font>

42
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't joke...</font>

43
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I say this because I quite like
 your usual composure</font>

44
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and ability to maintain a professional 
detachment to your work,</font>

45
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">although you seem 
rather invested this time.</font>

46
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose so.</font>

47
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I would feel compelled to see 
this through to the very end</font>

48
00:02:43,350 --> 00:02:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">now that my own life has been targeted.</font>

49
00:02:47,650 --> 00:02:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To that end, I must drag the inner 
workings of the church into the light.</i></font>

50
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

51
00:02:55,950 --> 00:02:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me in detail.</font>

52
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

53
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:18,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ISEKAI OFFICE WORKER: THE OTHER WORLD'S
BOOKS DEPEND ON THE BEAN COUNTER</font>

54
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ONE WEEK LATER</font>

55
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You...</font>

56
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you weren't coming anymore!</font>

57
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:39,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 12: WE CORNERED HIM. AND THEN...</font>

58
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My inspection may be over,</font>

59
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but didn't I tell you we'd be 
running the private school?</font>

60
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just barge in! 
Get permission first!</font>

61
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From whom?</font>

62
00:04:43,370 --> 00:04:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you mean the bishop, I've already 
gotten his permission for this.</font>

63
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck? You seem perfectly fine...</font>

64
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

65
00:04:52,010 --> 00:04:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing!</font>

66
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, you're not doing anything until 
I check with Siegvold-sama first!</font>

67
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

68
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siegvold-sama is currently 
with a visitor. Leave.</font>

69
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's too important to see a mere servant</font>

70
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and tagalong from another 
world so casually.</font>

71
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's forbidden to discriminate based 
on birth or origin within the church!</font>

72
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

73
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, this guy...
I mean, this gentleman here</font>

74
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has been working to educate orphans</font>

75
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and common children
to broaden their horizons!</font>

76
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one of us is truly going 
against the teachings of Abran?!</font>

77
00:05:30,730 --> 00:05:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You little...</font>

78
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is all this commotion?</font>

79
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry, Siegvold-sama. Commander.</font>

80
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were in a meeting and these
 two insisted on interrupting...</font>

81
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was the one who summoned him.</font>

82
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

83
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late.</font>

84
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I?</font>

85
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selio, we will be heading to the 
prayer room. Call the children.</font>

86
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

87
00:05:58,260 --> 00:06:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Return to your post, Fredrik.</font>

88
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes...</font>

89
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, your complexion 
looks a lot better.</font>

90
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to your help.</font>

91
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean thanks to <i>my</i> help.</font>

92
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-san, that wasn't 
what I was referring to.</font>

93
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, the way you're talking...</font>

94
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We aren't at the mansion right now.</font>

95
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, you promised 
to call me by my name.</font>

96
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes. That's right, Siegvold-sama.</font>

97
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's strange for you to 
be so formal with me</font>

98
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and so familiar with a 
commander of a royal order.</font>

99
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

100
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hardly. I'm quite close
 with Aresh-san, so...</font>

101
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I address him as I do
 because we're friends.</font>

102
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't I be your friend, as well?</font>

103
00:06:55,890 --> 00:07:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to be friends? 
But our ranks are so different...</font>

104
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our ranks? All humans 
are equal before God.</font>

105
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Aresh-san?</font>

106
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondou-san!</font>

107
00:07:14,990 --> 00:07:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-san?</font>

108
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We ran into Selio-kun right 
as we were heading to pray!</font>

109
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, too, Aresh-san! 
Are you here to pray?</font>

110
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

111
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Yurius-sama?</font>

112
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is Aresh doing here?!</font>

113
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a long story.</font>

114
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, why is Shiraishi-san 
participating in prayer again?</font>

115
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aresh-san, I feel like we haven't 
seen each other in a while.</font>

116
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's been bothering me.</font>

117
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the purification complete,</font>

118
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm watching over her
 as I keep an eye on things.</font>

119
00:07:43,690 --> 00:07:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might this concern the barrier?</font>

120
00:07:46,910 --> 00:07:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know about the barrier?</font>

121
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, him.</font>

122
00:07:52,890 --> 00:07:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The source of the leak is 
obvious, since only members</i></font>

123
00:07:56,290 --> 00:07:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of the royal family and the bishop 
know about the magical energy</i></font>

124
00:07:59,490 --> 00:08:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>used to maintain the barrier 
over the royal capital.</i></font>

125
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had my subordinates investigate,</font>

126
00:08:05,380 --> 00:08:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there was no trace of Yua's magical 
energy in the pool used for the barrier.</font>

127
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's excellent information.</font>

128
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We weren't able to get very far on 
our end, so your intel is very helpful.</font>

129
00:08:15,610 --> 00:08:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it. Did you just rope me and 
Yua into some kind of scheme?</font>

130
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since you're already here, 
there's no harm in joining us.</font>

131
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really know who I am?!</font>

132
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've thought this for a while now,</font>

133
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I've never felt a shred
 of respect from you!</font>

134
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, he noticed?</i></font>

135
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is a saying among 
the people of my country:</font>

136
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"When needed, make use of anyone 
at hand, even your parents."</font>

137
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of country is that?!</font>

138
00:08:46,970 --> 00:08:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My and Shiraishi-san's homeland.</font>

139
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then so be it.</font>

140
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Yurius-sama.</font>

141
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to uncover the truth.</font>

142
00:09:05,590 --> 00:09:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you've also gotten quite close 
with His Highness while I was away.</font>

143
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what is it that you 
would like us to do?</font>

144
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just the usual prayer, Cipriano-san.</font>

145
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're counting on you.</font>

146
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, everyone, please line 
up before the sacred relic.</font>

147
00:09:26,090 --> 00:09:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

148
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

149
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A magic tool used to measure 
magical energy levels.</font>

150
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sorcery department 
asked me to do a test run.</font>

151
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Conducting such experiments 
during our sacred prayers is...</font>

152
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prayer is a demonstration 
of one's faith in Abran.</font>

153
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Acts that probe the depths of the 
heart are unfitting for the church.</font>

154
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. I'll allow it.</font>

155
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bishop!</font>

156
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Excellency!</font>

157
00:09:57,760 --> 00:10:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall prove to you that our church 
has nothing to hide, Your Excellency.</font>

158
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would be most appreciated.</font>

159
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cipriano.</font>

160
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

161
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let us begin the prayer.</font>

162
00:10:17,450 --> 00:10:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

163
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this supposed to tell us?</font>

164
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It shows the amount of magical 
energy offered this time.</font>

165
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what of it?</font>

166
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our prayers are something 
we offer to Abran!</font>

167
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incorrect. The magical energy
 offered in the name of Abran</font>

168
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is used to maintain the barrier 
that protects the royal capital.</font>

169
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this is the amount of magical 
energy used by that barrier.</font>

170
00:10:42,830 --> 00:10:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed. If you add it up, 
the monthly figures match.</font>

171
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course they do.</font>

172
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, it is our duty 
as citizens of this kingdom</font>

173
00:10:51,190 --> 00:10:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to offer the power of 
our prayers to our nation.</font>

174
00:10:56,490 --> 00:10:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Is there something else?</font>

175
00:10:59,020 --> 00:10:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

176
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are the magical energy readings
from prayer over the last three days.</font>

177
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the meaning of this?!</font>

178
00:11:07,450 --> 00:11:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just did the first 
reading a moment ago!</font>

179
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siegvold! You...</font>

180
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We completed the magical 
tool four days ago,</font>

181
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I've had Siegvold-san start taking 
measurements for the past three days.</font>

182
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see from the numbers,
the figures from the those days</font>

183
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are unmistakably higher than 
the reading taken today.</font>

184
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, now...</font>

185
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder where all that extra 
magical energy went.</font>

186
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any idea, Bishop?</font>

187
00:11:37,810 --> 00:11:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to my investigation,</font>

188
00:11:39,830 --> 00:11:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the holy maiden's magical energy 
wasn't used for the barrier.</font>

189
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You lot... Where did Yua's 
magical energy go?!</font>

190
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahem. These are the statistics 
on the magical energy consumed</font>

191
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by domestic industries during 
the current fiscal year.</font>

192
00:11:57,040 --> 00:12:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Upon investigating the suppliers 
responsible for this energy,</font>

193
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we discovered several entities whose 
actual existence could not be verified.</font>

194
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha—</font>

195
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, it's strange...</font>

196
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when comparing the 
magical energy purchases</font>

197
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">from these nonexistent 
vendors against the surplus,</font>

198
00:12:13,090 --> 00:12:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a slight excess remains unaccounted for.</font>

199
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

200
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I thought, Bishop Mateus 
seems completely unaware of it.</i></font>

201
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only a tiny amount each time,</font>

202
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if this occurs every month,</font>

203
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:27,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would accumulate to a considerable
 amount of magical energy.</font>

204
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world could you 
possibly be using it for...</font>

205
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cipriano-san?</font>

206
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cipriano-san?</font>

207
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cipriano.</font>

208
00:12:43,410 --> 00:12:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer him.</font>

209
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do with the magical energy
from the prayers of our holy believers?</font>

210
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy, you say?</font>

211
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't make me laugh!</font>

212
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Merke is the one and only true god!</font>

213
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A selfish little nobody like Abran 
can hardly be called a god!</font>

214
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a heretic!</font>

215
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Merke?</font>

216
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a deity worshipped in the East.</font>

217
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say she's the goddess of harmony</font>

218
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who repels enemies from other 
realms and the outside world.</font>

219
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enemies from other realms?</font>

220
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The holy maiden?! Purification?!</font>

221
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to top it off, the current holy 
maiden is from another world?</font>

222
00:13:30,090 --> 00:13:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forging a path to other worlds</font>

223
00:13:31,990 --> 00:13:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and destabilizing the balance is the 
very act that defiles our land!</font>

224
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abran himself is an evil deity! 
The real root of the miasma!</font>

225
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you?!</font>

226
00:13:41,590 --> 00:13:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abran blessed this kingdom 
with fertile lands.</font>

227
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not speak such sacrilege!</font>

228
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of fertility god is he?</font>

229
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A god who can only grant 
peace and fertile lands</font>

230
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for a mere hundred years 
or so is no god at all!</font>

231
00:13:56,350 --> 00:13:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You fiend!</font>

232
00:13:58,730 --> 00:14:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou, get behind me.</font>

233
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You fool.</font>

234
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you ask me what I used 
the magical energy for?</font>

235
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was this.</font>

236
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sense a high concentration 
of magical energy...</font>

237
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That thing is going to explode!</font>

238
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh... Not again...</i></font>

239
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to be saved yet again...</i></font>

240
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though...</i></font>

241
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want you to get hurt, either!</i></font>

242
00:14:45,290 --> 00:14:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

243
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! I did it!</font>

244
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yua?</font>

245
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What did you...</font>

246
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yua, isn't that dangerous?</font>

247
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's safe now.</font>

248
00:14:59,980 --> 00:15:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought it would be bad if it exploded,</font>

249
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I wrapped it in my magical 
energy and contained it.</font>

250
00:15:05,590 --> 00:15:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something like that even possible?</font>

251
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

252
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that exactly what 
you did, Kondou-san?</font>

253
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

254
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, that barrier 
in the demon forest.</font>

255
00:15:16,260 --> 00:15:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of shielding the surroundings, 
you contained the source</font>

256
00:15:20,130 --> 00:15:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with a barrier to prevent
 the danger from getting out.</font>

257
00:15:23,110 --> 00:15:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

258
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I only suggested the idea. 
I didn't actually perform the spell.</font>

259
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

260
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were the one who thought it up</font>

261
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and took all the steps 
to make it a reality.</font>

262
00:15:35,830 --> 00:15:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that essentially the same 
thing as you doing it yourself?</font>

263
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that expression?</font>

264
00:15:44,450 --> 00:15:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what are you doing?</font>

265
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of the holy maiden 
and disciple chosen by Abran!</font>

266
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To reject such noble individuals...</font>

267
00:15:55,110 --> 00:15:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The teachings of Merke are truly 
exclusionary and misguided, Cipriano.</font>

268
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, every person should have the freedom 
to choose what they believe in.</font>

269
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disciple, what are you saying?</font>

270
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly.</font>

271
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it normal for there
 to be lots of gods?</font>

272
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Holiness?!</font>

273
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abran is the one and only true god!</font>

274
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surely, as the holy maiden, 
you know this best!</font>

275
00:16:21,650 --> 00:16:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would that be?</font>

276
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True, I was summoned to this world and 
blessed with the power of purification,</font>

277
00:16:27,610 --> 00:16:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but what does that have to do with 
the existence of other gods?</font>

278
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, while Abranism 
is its official religion,</font>

279
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Romany Kingdom doesn't 
prohibit other religions.</font>

280
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that right, Your Excellency?</font>

281
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

282
00:16:44,930 --> 00:16:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're willing to believe in Merke?</font>

283
00:16:49,730 --> 00:16:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Japan is a nation that believes 
in the concept of countless gods.</i></font>

284
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We believe in nothing, 
but we also believe in everything.</i></font>

285
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why we don't deny anything.</i></font>

286
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I <i>suppose</i> she exists.</font>

287
00:17:04,570 --> 00:17:05,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the extent of my feelings.</i></font>

288
00:17:07,370 --> 00:17:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're willing to forgive me...</font>

289
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an entirely different matter.</font>

290
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

291
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Embezzlement of donations 
and magical energy.</font>

292
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Attempted murder and 
destruction of property.</font>

293
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, you committed 
these acts in the presence</font>

294
00:17:23,120 --> 00:17:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the royal family, prime 
minister, and holy maiden.</font>

295
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're surely facing 
high treason, as well.</font>

296
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm certain posing as a follower of 
Abran will also add charges of fraud.</font>

297
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apart from high treason, you're also 
looking at blasphemy and lèse-majesté.</font>

298
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With that, my work at the 
church truly came to an end.</i></font>

299
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mateus was exiled to the borderlands,</i></font>

300
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and Cipriano was sentenced to spend 
the rest of his life in prison.</i></font>

301
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:01,260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ONE MONTH LATER</font>

302
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Big Brother Kondu!</font>

303
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sigma-kun. Are you visiting 
the sorcery department again?</font>

304
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Ist-san invited me over.</font>

305
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I thought of a new magic tool!</font>

306
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sigma-kun has received permission to 
frequent the royal sorcery department,</i></font>

307
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh?</font>

308
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What do you think?</font>

309
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and he's also attending 
the new private school.</i></font>

310
00:18:16,050 --> 00:18:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's awesome!</font>

311
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Due to an overwhelming 
influx of applicants,</i></font>

312
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:25,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the school has expanded its classes
beyond our original plans.</i></font>

313
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Yurius and Shiraishi-san are 
getting along surprisingly well.</i></font>

314
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu! Have you thought about becoming a 
civil servant directly under His Highness?</font>

315
00:18:36,390 --> 00:18:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't joke.</font>

316
00:18:38,300 --> 00:18:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you supposed
 to be busy or something?</font>

317
00:18:41,170 --> 00:18:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. That's exactly why I delegated my 
mathematics classes to my subordinates.</font>

318
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

319
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking forward to teaching you!</font>

320
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you do something?</font>

321
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my first time meeting him!</font>

322
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean you won't 
come here anymore?</font>

323
00:18:57,300 --> 00:19:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will. The private school 
is only just getting started.</font>

324
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see.</font>

325
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sei-san, you're really 
popular wherever you go.</font>

326
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

327
00:19:09,780 --> 00:19:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even on our way here...</font>

328
00:19:12,210 --> 00:19:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seichiro!</font>

329
00:19:13,810 --> 00:19:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you leave the 
accounting department and serve as</font>

330
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the legal department's accountant
or start your own unit?</font>

331
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must politely decline...</font>

332
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichiro-san.</font>

333
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siegvold-san?</font>

334
00:19:28,140 --> 00:19:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Due to the recent incident, 
my family has asked me to return home.</font>

335
00:19:33,950 --> 00:19:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That crest is of the Aelvaar marquisate,
the family that donated to the church</i></font>

336
00:19:38,870 --> 00:19:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>magnitudes more than anyone else.</i></font>

337
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, I still wish to serve 
the god I've placed my faith in.</font>

338
00:19:46,570 --> 00:19:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I've also realized that 
I need to broaden my horizons.</font>

339
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please come to see me
whenever you visit the church.</font>

340
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

341
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou, let's go home.</font>

342
00:20:06,770 --> 00:20:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for me...</i></font>

343
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I plan to return to Japan eventually.</i></font>

344
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you received offers from both the 
prime minister and His Highness today.</font>

345
00:20:20,690 --> 00:20:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're certainly quick with the news.</font>

346
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I should inform you
that I turned them both down.</font>

347
00:20:25,810 --> 00:20:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, the way you're talking...</font>

348
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't reached the house yet.</font>

349
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he a little kid?</i></font>

350
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know if reciprocating Aresh-san's 
feelings is the right thing to do,</i></font>

351
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but...</i></font>

352
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once it gets a little warmer, why don't 
we take a trip to a seaside town?</font>

353
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you suddenly bringing that up?</font>

354
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a sea?</font>

355
00:20:52,180 --> 00:20:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. That is where my 
family's main estate lies.</font>

356
00:20:55,710 --> 00:20:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a villa on the grounds,</font>

357
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:59,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we can relax away from prying eyes.</font>

358
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You work too much, so it would be best 
to physically separate you from work.</font>

359
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go again...</font>

360
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

361
00:21:08,630 --> 00:21:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not until you reach a certain
milestone in your work.</font>

362
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't make you abandon 
your work halfway through.</font>

363
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Seiichirou?! 
Are you in pain somewhere?!</font>

364
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There he goes again!</i></font>

365
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How is he the Ice Nobleman? 
A black beast?</i></font>

366
00:21:33,850 --> 00:21:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fine. I admit it.</i></font>

367
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stop always being on the
receiving end of affection and protection.</i></font>

368
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-san.</font>

369
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? Do you want 
to go back to the infirmary?</font>

370
00:21:51,030 --> 00:21:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The two of us should discuss 
the future together.</i></font>

371
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

372
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kararapui. It's a dish from my homeland. 
We eat it during celebrations.</font>

373
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou, what's wrong?</font>

374
00:22:18,050 --> 00:22:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a fever?</font>

375
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm not sick.</font>

376
00:22:22,380 --> 00:22:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just a little embarrassed.</font>

377
00:22:25,670 --> 00:22:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Embarrassed? Why?</font>

378
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my country, we don't talk about 
matters of romance so openly...</font>

379
00:22:34,020 --> 00:22:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what it seemed 
like from your letter.</font>

380
00:22:37,190 --> 00:22:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I'll inform Valtom.</font>

381
00:22:42,410 --> 00:22:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What letter?</font>

382
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your reply to me.</font>

383
00:22:48,430 --> 00:22:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reply? Wait... No way!</font>

384
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Did you read it?!</font>

385
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a letter addressed to me.</font>

386
00:22:58,920 --> 00:23:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with me 
opening and reading it?</font>

387
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Even as a landlord, 
you shouldn't rummage</font>

388
00:23:03,660 --> 00:23:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">through my desk without permission!</font>

389
00:23:06,010 --> 00:23:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't me.</font>

390
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Valtom was the one who gave it to me.</font>

391
00:23:11,190 --> 00:23:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was this while I was hospitalized?</i></font>

392
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No wonder Aresh-san didn't seem to be 
in a bad mood when I was discharged!</i></font>

393
00:23:20,130 --> 00:23:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give it back.</font>

394
00:23:21,950 --> 00:23:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a letter to me, so it's mine.</font>

395
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't send it to you, 
so it's still mine!</font>

396
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already received it, so it's mine.</font>

